  "prompt": "What are the top 5 headphones under Rs.1000 in India?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2021, prices and product availability can vary, but I can suggest some popular headphones that have typically been well-received in the under Rs. 1000 category in India. However, you should check the latest reviews and price listings to ensure they still fit your budget and requirements. Here are five options that were commonly recommended:\n\n1. **Boat Bassheads 100**:\n   - Known for good bass and sound quality.\n   - Comfortable design with in-line microphone.\n   - Good build quality for the price.\n\n2. **Zebronics Zeb-Rush**:\n   - Features a stylish design and decent sound quality.\n   - Foldable and portable, with a built-in mic.\n   - Good for music and calling in this price range.\n\n3. **Sony MDR-EX150AP**:\n   - Offers good sound quality with a balanced output.\n   - Comes with a built-in mic and an ergonomic design.\n   - Reliable choice from a reputable brand.\n\n4. **Redgear Cloak Wired RGB Gaming Headphones**:\n   - Popular among gamers for decent sound and build quality.\n   - Features RGB lighting and a comfortable fit.\n   - Good mic quality for gaming and calling.\n\n5. **Kotion Each GS410**:\n   - Widely used for gaming, offering good sound and comfort.\n   - Features a noise-isolating microphone.\n   - Compatible with multiple devices, including PCs and consoles.\n\nPlease verify current prices and user reviews before making a purchase, as models and availability can change frequently.",
